OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778198576
OL,3,CVoting for 2026 elections is underway
OL,4,C- but why won't you hear much from us?
OL,6,FIt's election day in England,
OL,7,FScotland, and Wales, and voters are
OL,8,Fcasting their ballots in a series of
OL,9,Flocal, mayoral, and national elections.
OL,11,FIf you have got used to hearing
OL,12,Fregular coverage of the political
OL,13,Fcampaigns, you might notice a
OL,14,Fdifference from broadcasters on
OL,15,Fpolling day.
OL,17,FStrict rules exist to govern what
OL,18,Fbroadcasters can and cannot air while
OL,19,Fpeople cast their votes to ensure that
OL,20,Felections run fairly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
