CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778198576
OL,3,CVoting for 2026 elections is underway
OL,4,C- but why won't you hear much from us?
OL,6,FBroadcasters are not allowed to air
OL,7,Fany discussion or analysis of election
OL,8,Fand referendum issues during the times
OL,9,Fin which polls are open.
OL,11,FThis is typically 7 am, but due to +1
OL,12,Fchannels, TV broadcasters end this
OL,13,Fcoverage at 6 am.
OL,15,FIt is equally an offence to air exit
OL,16,Fand opinion polls before polls close
OL,17,Fat 10 pm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
