PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778198576
OL,3,CVoting for 2026 elections is underway
OL,4,C- but why won't you hear much from us?
OL,6,FNo major polling authority has
OL,7,Fannounced its intention to conduct an
OL,8,Fexit poll at the local elections - in
OL,9,Fpractice, some parties commission
OL,10,Ftheir own.
OL,12,FThe rules are designed to ensure
OL,13,Ffairness and make sure no one watching
OL,14,For listening to the news on polling
OL,15,Fday has their vote influenced or
OL,16,Fdecides not to vote at all.
OL,18,FBroadcasters will still mention the
OL,19,Felections, but must stick to basic
OL,20,Ffacts such as where and when political
OL,21,Fleaders voted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
