OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778198576
OL,3,CVoting for 2026 elections is underway
OL,4,C- but why won't you hear much from us?
OL,6,FPolitical stories that arise on the
OL,7,Fday and are not related to the
OL,8,Felections can be covered as well as
OL,9,Fanything directly linked to the
OL,10,Fprocess of polling day that may help
OL,11,Fviewers and listeners.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThe law doesn't cover posts already
OL,19,Fmade before polling day, so we do not
OL,20,Fhave to remove pieces covering the
OL,21,Felection prior to Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
