OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778198576
OL,3,CVoting for 2026 elections is underway
OL,4,C- but why won't you hear much from us?
OL,6,FThere are, however, further rules
OL,7,Fwhich help broadcasters ensure fair
OL,8,Fcoverage in the run-up to elections.
OL,10,FThese are designed to ensure all
OL,11,Fparties receive a fair amount of
OL,12,Fcoverage and include rules such as
OL,13,Fwhen reporting in a constituency, if
OL,14,Fone candidate is invited to
OL,15,Fparticipate, all candidates must be
OL,16,Fextended the same offer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
