CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778198576
OL,3,CVoting for 2026 elections is underway
OL,4,C- but why won't you hear much from us?
OL,6,FSimilarly, if a candidate is mentioned
OL,7,Fin a news report, viewers and
OL,8,Flisteners must be signposted to where
OL,9,Fthey can see a full list of candidates
OL,10,Fstanding in that area.
OL,12,FBroadcasters must always ensure
OL,13,Fbalance and impartiality in their
OL,14,Fcoverage as per the OFCOM guidelines.
OL,15,FThis remains the case during
OL,16,Felections, but additional measures are
OL,17,Fimplemented to ensure fairness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
